\title{Photodissociation of trapped Rb$_2^+$: Implications for hybrid molecular ion-atom trapping}
\author{S. Jyothi$^1$, Tridib Ray$^{1,2}$, Sourav Dutta$^1$, A.R. Allouche$^3$, Romain Vexiau$^4$, Olivier Dulieu$^4$ and S. A. Rangwala$^1$}
